WEBVTT

00:00.910 --> 00:02.180
<i>Previously on Kyle XY...</i>

00:02.210 --> 00:03.750
My mom and I talked,

00:03.780 --> 00:05.380
She won't let me see you outside
of school for awhile.

00:05.410 --> 00:06.380
She could be you.

00:06.410 --> 00:07.410
What?

00:07.450 --> 00:08.710
The two of you

00:08.750 --> 00:10.610
Used to play that song all the time.

00:10.650 --> 00:11.610
It's not there.

00:11.650 --> 00:13.610
It's their song, D4,

00:13.650 --> 00:15.150
It's the missing record from the jukebox.

00:15.180 --> 00:16.650
Where did you get this?

00:16.680 --> 00:18.150
I found it in my room.

00:18.180 --> 00:20.080
I'm trying to book the DJ for an event.

00:20.110 --> 00:21.310
A prom?

00:21.350 --> 00:22.410
You're DJ Spinbrandt?

00:22.450 --> 00:24.350
And I don't do proms.

00:24.380 --> 00:26.480
Oh my god, I can't believe I got
into this whole mess over you!

00:26.510 --> 00:27.850
How sweet is this?

00:27.880 --> 00:29.180
That's awesome.

00:29.210 --> 00:30.680
You're awesome.

00:30.710 --> 00:32.350
You're kind of awesome, too.

00:32.380 --> 00:34.580
Maybe I am lazy and I lack study skills,

00:34.610 --> 00:36.280
but I've changed,

00:36.310 --> 00:37.880
And I'm going to do something
important with my life

00:37.910 --> 00:39.050
and make a difference.

00:39.080 --> 00:40.110
You don't know how Sarah died.

00:40.150 --> 00:41.250
She was just like you.

00:41.280 --> 00:43.250
Trying too much, too fast,

00:43.280 --> 00:45.780
and when she tried something she
wasn't ready for, it killed her.

00:45.810 --> 00:47.480
You can't keep doing this to yourself.

00:47.510 --> 00:48.550
Promise me you'll stop.

00:50.910 --> 00:52.150
I promise...

00:52.180 --> 00:54.010
I'm going in for my check-up tomorrow,

00:54.050 --> 00:55.880
It'll tell me if I'm better or not.

00:55.910 --> 00:57.780
Andy, everything's going to be okay.

00:59.550 --> 01:01.180
You know, when you say it,

01:01.210 --> 01:03.650
I almost believe it.

